name: ALESSO x ROUGH DRAFT I
description: Chapter I is the opening scene of your cosmic odyssey. Follow the shining star through the cosmos to the sounds of your galactic DJ, Alesso. Where will this sci-fi saga take you? Subsequent Chapters II-IV await, and with them a revealing big bang on November 4 at Dreamverse, presented by Metapurse. PLUS, each token grants ( 1 ) entry for a chance to win a ticket on a ride to the edge-of-space courtesy of World View in 2024!
